kcheckgmail (0.5.7.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream version
    - Several enhacements and bug fixes
    - Man page is now provided by upstream, dropping debian/additions/kcheckgmail.1
  * Changed the menu entry from Apps/Net to Applications/Network/Communication to accomplish with the new Debian menu subpolicy
  * Prevent dh_compress from compressing the docbook
  * Replaced -$(MAKE) distclean with [ ! -f Makefile ] || $(MAKE) distclean
  * Adding myself as co-maintainer
  * debian/rules is now DEB_BUILD_OPTIONS=debug aware
  * Fixed debian/watch so it correctly reports new upstream versions

 -- Raphael Geissert <atomo64@gmail.com>  Wed, 05 Sep 2007 16:24:00 -0500

